{"tid":2230833,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"香港僱主正正正仆街","createTime":"2020-10-05T08:05:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T13:55:14.000Z","uid":73269,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"bcb3302d7a99ec60f88775374cb0ecfc554c9e54","tid":2230833,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T08:05:37.000Z","msg":"今日全港大塞車<br />\n之前乜q顏色大雨<br />\n同埋 革命+疫情<br />\n都要返工<br />\n<br />\n呢啲事件<br />\n當然有人遲到㗎喇<br />\n當年亦有人 天跌落嚟 永遠唔遲到啦<br />\n<br />\n今日啲仆街管理層又開會<br />\n好似要應變緊急事故嘅影響<br />\n叫全部人以後「 提早」15分鐘「 準時」 返工<br />\n呢個方案 <br />\n已經用過兩次<br />\n本來合約上面寫九點十五分上班<br />\n<br />\n而家八點半就要返到公司， 準備九點15分返工<br />\n<br />\n你質疑佢呢個決定佢就答你<br />\n永遠都係有準備好過冇準備<br />\n<br />\n唔遲到嘅同事就係因為有準備<br />\n而家公司嘅決定係幫助你哋做好準備"},{"pid":"61ee7357a3455d63618ad7a4706a2ff68f154087","tid":2230833,"uid":252142,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T09:00:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"848b4100bf96be5c27e6070c8f62ce7cac38f0ff","tid":2230833,"uid":13518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T09:01:25.000Z","msg":"慘撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09b361ccade43dbcaaa84b345c179ce5cac231e8","tid":2230833,"uid":154373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T09:05:11.000Z","msg":"有無諗過係你班奴隸種出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又唔肯反抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67abe2ac5f6b2bcc5ef1635a5385d47b4dcfa46d","tid":2230833,"uid":56428,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09b361ccade43dbcaaa84b345c179ce5cac231e8","tid":2230833,"uid":154373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T09:05:11.000Z","msg":"有無諗過係你班奴隸種出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又唔肯反抗<img src=\"/assets/faces